<h2>Why This Blog Exists</h2>

<p>
This blog is my learning journal, technical portfolio, and a place where I document real-world projects, lessons learned, and experiments across Cloud, DevOps, Linux, Embedded Systems, and IoT.
</p>

<blockquote>

Technology creates the greatest impact when software, hardware, cloud infrastructure, and people work together to solve meaningful problems.

</blockquote>

<p>

Thanks for stopping by. I hope my journey inspires others who are transitioning into technology or building practical engineering skills.

</p>

